---------------
CS Boomerang Supplies HDR
===============

Map for CS Source
by Harrison 26 


Terrorists : Hold the hostages, or kill all the Counter-Terrorists.


Counter-Terrorists : Kill all Terrorists, or rescue hostages. 
There are 3 hostages, take care of them!

---------------
Story:

Terrorists have been spotted by a security guard stealing
supplies from Boomerang Supplies. Hostages have been 
taken and the Terrorists demands are unrealistic. It is time
for the Counter-Terrorist unit to take control.

--------------
New to this version:
Now features HDR graphics, improved gameplay, new skybox, and improved performance!
